TEST get_user_success

RECEIVE HTTP:GET /api/v1/users/42
HEADERS
  Authorization: Bearer token_abc123xyz

EXPECT READ:MYSQL users
USING_SQL """
SELECT users.* FROM `users` WHERE `users`.`token` = 'token_abc123xyz' LIMIT 1
"""
RETURNS {{payloads/user_response.json}}

EXPECT READ:MYSQL users
USING_SQL """
SELECT users.* FROM `users` WHERE `users`.`id` = 42 LIMIT 1
"""
RETURNS {{payloads/user_response.json}}

RESPOND HTTP:200
WITH {{payloads/user_public_response.json}}
